Whoa, that's going
to attract seagulls.

16:37.423 --> 16:40.691
Okay, let's get this over with.

16:40.692 --> 16:43.560
Don't you want to have some room
service champagne and oysters?

16:43.561 --> 16:45.695
No. I do this better
on an empty stomach.

16:47.364 --> 16:50.300
By the way, um, I'm a little
foggy from the Vicodin,

16:50.301 --> 16:52.436
so if I fall asleep in the middle,

16:52.437 --> 16:54.871
just give me a little
tap on the shoulder.

16:54.872 --> 16:56.440
Okay.

16:56.441 --> 16:58.308
Come here.

17:00.909 --> 17:02.575
You're a good kisser, Alan.

17:02.576 --> 17:04.076
Thank you.

17:04.077 --> 17:05.811
Better than my ex-husband.

17:05.813 --> 17:09.781
Oh. Well, good for me.

17:09.782 --> 17:11.750
He made up for it

17:11.751 --> 17:13.952
below the waist,
if you know what I mean.

17:15.421 --> 17:17.622
He had big feet?

17:17.623 --> 17:19.022
Three of them.

17:19.023 --> 17:21.625
But only two wore shoes.

17:22.894 --> 17:24.962
Lucky you.

17:24.963 --> 17:26.463
Ah, don't worry.

17:26.464 --> 17:28.397
Size doesn't matter to me.

17:28.398 --> 17:29.799
Good to know.

17:29.800 --> 17:32.534
In fact, in this situation,

17:32.535 --> 17:34.770
the smaller the better.

17:39.775 --> 17:43.143
Um... you're welcome?

17:51.051 --> 17:52.517
What the hell was that?

17:52.518 --> 17:53.919
Um, I don't know.

17:53.920 --> 17:56.521
Maybe the strawberries are
fighting with the oysters.

18:00.091 --> 18:02.526
Uh-oh.

18:02.527 --> 18:03.960
What?

18:03.961 --> 18:05.661
I think the oysters are
making a break for it.

18:05.662 --> 18:07.864
Excuse me.

18:08.766 --> 18:10.033
Are you going to throw up?

18:10.034 --> 18:11.300
I wish!

18:11.301 --> 18:14.036
You might want to
turn the TV on-- loud!

18:14.037 --> 18:15.938
Why?

18:15.939 --> 18:18.406
You don't want to hear
what's about to happen!

18:18.407 --> 18:22.143
♪ Oh... klahoma ♪

18:22.144 --> 18:25.113
♪ Where the wind comes
sweeping down the plain ♪

18:25.114 --> 18:27.014
♪ Where the waving wheat ♪

18:27.015 --> 18:29.782
♪ It sure smells sweet
when the wind... ♪

18:29.783 --> 18:31.983
♪ <i>Men.</i> ♪

18:31.984 --> 18:33.317
All right, one grilled cheese

18:33.318 --> 18:35.386
with avocado and bacon,
extra crispy.

18:35.387 --> 18:37.554
Oh, thank you, honey.

18:37.555 --> 18:39.723
You realize that bacon's
going to kill you.

18:39.724 --> 18:42.225
I know.

18:42.226 --> 18:44.627
You say you know,
but you keep eating it.

18:44.628 --> 18:46.628
Oh, come on, don't nag.

18:46.629 --> 18:48.963
I'm not nagging,
I'm concerned about you.

18:48.964 --> 18:51.232
Fine, fine.
I'll take the bacon off.

18:51.233 --> 18:52.701
Don't do me any favors.

18:52.702 --> 18:54.903
No-no, no. I'm doing it.
I'm doing it, see?

19:01.243 --> 19:02.810
Who's that?

19:02.811 --> 19:04.711
Just the kid. Jake, get in here!

19:04.712 --> 19:06.246
We have a kid?

19:06.247 --> 19:08.014
You didn't say anything
about having a kid.

19:08.015 --> 19:10.116
He's not ours. He's my brother's.

19:10.117 --> 19:13.385
So what's my part in
<i>this</i> scenario?

19:13.386 --> 19:16.554
You don't think I'm a good role model,
and yet, paradoxically,

19:16.555 --> 19:18.489
you still want to
have children with me.

19:19.925 --> 19:21.258
What?

19:21.259 --> 19:24.027
Did you go out even
though you were grounded?

19:24.028 --> 19:25.895
You told me to.

19:25.896 --> 19:29.198
Don't look at me like that.
He's lying.

19:29.199 --> 19:30.399
I'm not lying.

19:30.400 --> 19:32.567
And I'm not looking at you.

19:32.568 --> 19:34.168
All right, all right, enough.

19:34.169 --> 19:36.103
You, young man,

19:36.104 --> 19:37.905
go to your room and think
about what you've done.

19:37.906 --> 19:39.873
Whatever.

19:41.208 --> 19:43.509
I think we handled
that really well.

19:43.510 --> 19:45.711
Tough love, but I'm
still the cool uncle.

19:45.712 --> 19:48.246
Hey, if you're happy, I'm happy.

19:49.148 --> 19:50.615
I'm very happy.

19:50.616 --> 19:52.150
In fact, are you free tomorrow?

19:52.151 --> 19:54.919
I'm never free, but I'm available.

19:54.920 --> 19:56.353
Well, great.

19:56.354 --> 19:58.389
How about you drag me
to some boring museum

19:58.390 --> 19:59.856
so I can miss the Laker game?

20:02.159 --> 20:03.393
It's your money.

20:03.394 --> 20:05.061
Is it okay if I go take a shower?

20:05.062 --> 20:06.128
Well, sure. Okay.

20:06.129 --> 20:07.630
I'll be up in a bit.

20:14.336 --> 20:16.770
Still cheaper than getting married.

20:18.072 --> 20:20.707
♪ <i>Men.</i> ♪

20:23.507 --> 20:25.842
All righty. Here we are.

20:26.743 --> 20:28.944
Thank you. You're welcome.

20:30.480 --> 20:35.751
Believe it or not,
I actually had a good time.

20:35.752 --> 20:39.386
Nice hotel, room service,
no teenagers.

20:39.387 --> 20:41.621
Um, I'm glad.

20:41.622 --> 20:44.057
So, shall we try it again

20:44.058 --> 20:47.960
in, you know, five or six days?

20:47.961 --> 20:50.862
I would like that.

20:54.166 --> 20:55.433
Okay, uh...

20:55.434 --> 20:56.834
I don't mean to rush you,
but I really

20:56.835 --> 20:58.569
have to go home to my bathroom.

20:58.570 --> 20:59.837
Want to use mine?

20:59.838 --> 21:01.271
Uh, no. No, that wouldn't

21:01.272 --> 21:03.373
be good for our relationship.

21:03.374 --> 21:04.574
All right.

21:04.575 --> 21:05.975
Well, bye.

21:05.976 --> 21:07.476
Seriously, get out of the car.

